    "body": "Since docker runs on another virtual machine, it has a different IP address and networking. The loopback address `127.0.0.1` will point to the docker machine, not the host machine.  \r\n\r\nYou have two options:\r\n- Use LAN IP address instead of 127.0.0.1\r\n- Add `--network host` to have the docker container run using the host's networking. This would allow 127.0.0.1 to reference the host loopback address. ",
